creator: Football Sessions
descriptionHtml:
Featuring a player report creation tool branded with club identity and a range of in-depth age specific goalkeeping drills, Football Sessions - Goalkeeping gives goalkeeper football coaches of all abilities, resources to inspire delivery at every session.

Coaches can create three types of goalkeeper report with specialised prompts to guide an accurate assessment. Completed reports are sent direct to our free Football Sessions – Player app. Additionally, reports can be sent to club technical directors to assess their goalkeeper talent.

Both the report score criteria and the goalkeeper training sessions are based on the globally-accepted Four Corner player development model and talent identification profiling system.

The extensive range of goalkeeping drills can also be filtered by ability level. Goalkeeper coaches can build and save multi-layered sessions from warm up, conditioning, to phases of play and small sided games.

The goalkeeper practices, the report generator and resources are tailored for all levels of coach and player with specialised areas for high performance football.

While perfectly suited to individual coaches looking for a particular goalkeeping drill, the app can also provide Club Academy Managers and Technical Directors with a consistent programme and player reporting feature for all their coaching staff.

The reporting feature and the app content has been developed by UEFA and AFC professionals with playing, coaching, coach education and game management experience from grassroots to pro-level.

The app is compatible for use on phone and tablet.

Feedback welcome to help us create more useful tips and tools.
descriptionShort: Ultimate tool for football (soccer) goalkeeping coaches - drills and reporting.
